headline: Intuit (INTU) Slipped as the Outlook and Guidance Fell Short of Expectations
summary: Bristol Gate Capital Partners, an investment management company, published its Q3 2025 investor letter for the “US Equity Strategy”. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here.
